---
title: All-American Beef Burger with Beetroot Relish, Smokey Aioli & Herbed Fries
description: This classic burger becomes next-level-delicious with the addition of smokey aioli slathered over toasty baked buns. With sweet
beetroot relish, a moreish beef patty and oven-baked herby fries, we're tipping it'll become your new burger craving!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/all-american-beef-burger-e01046aa.jpg
